                  <p>This folder contains photographic reproductions of early (16th and 17th century) German bookplates as well as inscriptions or other related artwork. Some of the black-and-white photographs bear annotations, including blazons or descriptions of the coats of arms, as well as other notes, possible references to numbers from the Franks Collection, etc.</p>
